- Three key evidence points: (1) AI challenged long-held antipodal paradigms (paper); (2) "interpreting the data from the AI black box" was the hardest work—解释神 (PKU video ~15:22); (3) second agent design came from human instinct to manually delete bad entries in 14D (PKU video ~09:35).
